<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 63. Clubiona spp. of the C. corticalis group, male palp, retrolateral view A C. cochlearis B C. rama C C. subrama D C. zhigangi sp. nov., holotype. Abbreviations: C = conductor; E = embolus; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis; VTA = ventral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figure 81. Clubiona spp. of the C. corticalis group, epigyne, cleared, ventral view A C. cochlearis B C. dengpao sp. nov., holotype C C. yejiei sp. nov., holotype D C. tixing sp. nov., holotype E C. subrama F C. zhigangi sp. nov., paratype. Abbreviations: A = atrium; AM = atrial membrane; CO = copulatory opening. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figure 73. Clubiona spp. of the C. corticalis group, epigyne, intact, ventral view A C. cochlearis B C. dengpao sp. nov., holotype C C. yejiei sp. nov., holotype D C. tixing sp. nov., holotype E C. subrama F C. zhigangi sp. nov., paratype. Abbreviations: A = atrium; AM = atrial membrane; CO = copulatory opening. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figure 89. Clubiona spp. of the C. corticalis group, vulva, cleared dorsal view A C. cochlearis B C. dengpao sp. nov., holotype C C. yejiei sp. nov., holotype D C. tixing sp. nov., holotype E C. subrama F C. zhigangi sp. nov., paratype. Abbreviations: BS = bursa; CD = copulatory duct; FD = fertilisation duct; SH = spermathecal head; SP = spermatheca. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figure 53. Clubiona spp. of the C. corticalis group, male palp, ventral view A C. cochlearis B C. rama C C. subrama D C. zhigangi sp. nov., holotype. Abbreviations: C = conductor; E = embolus. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535482" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535472" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535498" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535462" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535490" .

